'''热带风暴马可'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Marco}}）是[[信史|有纪录以来]]地球上规模最小的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年大西洋飓风季]]第13场获得命名的风暴。系统源于2008年9月下旬[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]西北部上空的广阔[[低气压|低气压区]]。10月4日，受[[东风波|东风波]]影响，[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]上空发展出小规模[[大气环流|下层环流]]。低气压区从[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]最南端掠过并进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]，于10月6日发展成本季第十三号热带低气压{{#tag:ref|根据[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的定义，热带低气压是指[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]在每小时62公里以下的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}。低气压很快就于当晚增强成热带风暴并获名“马可”{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，再于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月7日清晨达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里的最高强度{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有风速数据均为1分钟持续风速。|group="注"|name="winds"}}。

达到最高强度时，马可的热带风暴强度风场仅从[[风眼|中心]]向四周延伸18.5公里，创下规模最小热带气旋的新纪录并保持至今<ref name="FAQ">{{cite web | author = Neal Dorst | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Subject: E5) Which are the largest and smallest tropical cyclones on record? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040433/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E5.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E5.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] }}</ref><ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = James L. Franklin | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Marco | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-11-04 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011329/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132008_Marco.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132008_Marco.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。协调世界时中午12点左右，气旋从墨西哥[[韋拉克鲁斯州|韋拉克鲁斯州]]的米桑特拉附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，然后就开始迅速减弱，于当天晚上逐渐消散。由于覆盖范围很小，马可造成的破坏程度很轻，但气旋产生的暴雨引发3米多深的汹涌洪水，造成多户民居受损，另有多条公路被淹。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Marco 2008 track.png}}
2008年9月下旬，[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]西北部上空有广阔的[[低气压|低气压区]]持续存在，这里便是热带风暴马可的起源。10月4日，有[[东风波|东风波]]到达相应海域，系统在[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]上空催生出[[大气环流|环流中心]]。由于太接近陆地，低气压区起初难以发展。逼近[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]后，低气压区周围迅速发展出[[对流|对流]]。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月6日凌晨0点，低气压区在[[特尔米诺斯泻湖|特尔米诺斯泻湖]]上空发展成[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年大西洋飓风季]]的第十三号热带低气压。<ref name="TCR" />受北侧的中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，低气压总体向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动。由于气旋行经洋面[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]环境好，[[风切变|风切变]]少而且[[海面温度|水温]]偏高，气象机构预计系统会得以增强。<ref name="D1">{{cite report | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Discussion One | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034601/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.001.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]{{#tag:ref|美国国家飓风中心是[[大西洋|大西洋]]的[[区域专责气象中心|区域专责气象中心]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Christopher W. Landsea | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2014 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Subject: F1) What regions around the globe have tropical cyclones and who is responsible for forecasting there? | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/F1.html | archivedate = 2015-03-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326101039/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/F1.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。|group="注"|name="NHC"}}于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天中午12点将规模很小、云系覆盖范围宽度不超过137公里的热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“马可”（{{lang|en|Marco}}）命名<ref name="TCR" />。

由于外界环境有利，马可在10月6日得以[[快速增强|迅速强化]]。10月7日清晨，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]飞入风暴后测得飞行高度层风速达每小时110公里，地面风速每小时98公里，据此推算气旋已达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]105公里、最低[[气压|气压]]998[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]；29.47 [[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]<!-- {{convert/dual|998|mbar|kPa|inHg|abbr=on|lk=on}} -->）的最高强度。<ref name="TCR" />随着马可的强度迅速提高，气象机构认为风暴有可能在登陆前达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|飓风标准]]{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，飓风是指持续风速在每小时119公里或以上的大西洋和东北太平洋热带气旋，这一标准与西太平洋的[[台风|台风]]相同<ref name="glos">{{cite report | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="D2">{{cite web | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223647/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.002.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Marco Discussion Two | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋继续向西北偏西方向前进，其内部有小规模深层对流保持，覆盖范围平均直径仅有14.8公里<ref name="D3">{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-07 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100621/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.003.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Marco Discussion Three | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。达到最高强度后不久，马可的热带风暴强度风场从中心向外的扩展半径也只有18.5公里<ref name="D5">{{cite web | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-07 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Tropical Storm Marco Discussion Five | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.005.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220743/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月7日中午12点，马可的中心从墨西哥[[韋拉克鲁斯州|韋拉克鲁斯州]]的米桑特拉（{{lang|en|Misantla}}）附近登陆，登陆时的风力时速为105公里，仍处最高强度<ref name="TCR" />。进入陆地上空后，气旋迅速弱化<ref name="D6">{{cite web | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-07 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Tropical Depression Marco Discussion Six | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111254/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.discus.006.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，登陆仅6小时后就降级成热带低气压，最终于当晚在墨西哥山区上空逐渐消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施、影响和纪录 ==
{{See also|热带气旋警告}}
[[File:Marco_Norber_Odile_10-6-08_2245Z.jpg|left]]（左下方）、热带风暴马可，以及之后会发展成[[2008年热带风暴奥迪尔|热带风暴奥迪尔]]的低气压区（中下）同时存在。]]
风暴形成之时，墨西哥政府向韋拉克鲁斯州[[图斯潘|图斯潘]]（{{lang|en|Tuxpan}}）到蓬塔拉戛托（{{lang|en|Punta El Lagarto}}）之间的[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]沿岸地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="public01">{{cite report | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Public Advisory One | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202921/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.public.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.public.001.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。当天下午，该国政府又向卡沃罗霍（{{lang|en|Cabo Rojo}}）到[[韋拉克鲁斯_(韋拉克鲁斯州)|韋拉克鲁斯]]之间地区发布飓风警告，同时把前述热带风暴警告的生效范围向北面延伸至卡沃罗霍<ref name="public02">{{cite report | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Jamie Rhome | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Tropical Storm Marco Public Advisory Two | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.public.002.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234724/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al13/al132008.public.002.shtml }}</ref>。政府部门赶在风暴来袭前开设200个避难所，并将多所学校关闭。估计海岸沿线的低洼地区共有约3000人撤离<ref name="MSNBC1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305095014/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/27055334/wid/16438329 | deadurl = no | publisher = [[MSNBC|NBCNews.com]] | title = Tropical Storm Marco hits Mexico's Gulf coast | date = 2008-10-08 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/27055334/wid/16438329 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>，墨西哥军人动用校车将疏散居民送到避难所<ref name="USAT1" />。马可成形所在海域当时有多个墨西哥主要石油设施<ref name="Marco forms near oil fields">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015612/http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-mexico-storm-idUKTRE49582320081006 | url = http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-mexico-storm-idUKTRE49582320081006 | title = Tropical storm Marco forms near Mexico oil fields | author = Robert Campbell | date = 2008-10-06 | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>，有4个石油平台上的33名工作人员撤离。此外，韋拉克鲁斯州还有6口油井和1家[[天然气|天然气]]处理厂关闭<ref name="USAT1" />。经[[墨西哥交通运输部|墨西哥交通运输部]]下令，韋拉克鲁斯州[[瑙特拉_(韋拉克鲁斯州)|瑙特拉]]（{{lang|en|Nautla}}）和[[阿尔瓦拉多_(墨西哥)|阿尔瓦拉多]]（{{lang|en|Alvarado}}）的港口禁止小型船只进出，以防万一<ref name="USAT1">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | title = Tropical Storm Marco hits Mexico's Gulf coast | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201033/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2008-10-07-tropical-storm-marco_N.htm | url = https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2008-10-07-tropical-storm-marco_N.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date = 2008-10-07 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | publisher = Gannett Co. }}</ref>。

