风暴登陆后产生暴雨，[[圣路易斯波托西州|圣路易斯波托西州]]的普哈尔（{{lang|en|El Pujal}}）降下201毫米雨量，是全州降水最多的所在<ref>{{cite report | publisher = [[世界气象组织|World Meteorological Organization]] | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214031953/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC31/documents/Doc4.2-4_Mexico.doc | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = 41st Session Country Report: Mexico | archivedate = 2012-02-14 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC31/documents/Doc4.2-4_Mexico.doc | format = [[DOC格式|DOC]] | date =  }}</ref>，并且平均每小时的降雨量高达25.4毫米<!-- {{convert|1|in/h|mm/h}} --><ref name="TCR" />。韋拉克鲁斯附近多个沿海城镇发生洪灾，部分居民被迫向地势更高的地方转移<ref name="Marco lashes Mexico's Gulf coast">{{cite news | url = http://in.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-35845720081007 | title = Tropical Storm Marco lashes Mexico's Gulf coast | date = 2008-10-07 | agency = Reuters | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | archivedate = 2016-01-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125140816/http://in.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-35845720081007 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。墨西哥多地此前已饱受严重洪灾的摧残，这次马可产生的暴雨更是雪上加霜<ref name="USAT1" />。韋拉克鲁斯州政府在风暴过后的损失调查报告中表示，州内有两条河因这场风暴产生的雨水泛滥成灾<ref>{{cite press release | publisher = Government of Veracruz | date = 2008-10-07 | accessdate = 2009-08-15 | title = Press Release | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090815053904/http://sfpsys.sefiplan.gob.mx/aplicaciones/rss/Desplegar?articulo=4642 | url = http://sfpsys.sefiplan.gob.mx/aplicaciones/rss/Desplegar?articulo=4642 | archivedate = 2009-08-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。其中1条河导致包括[[米纳蒂特兰_(韋拉克鲁斯州)|米纳蒂特兰]]在内多个城镇的积水有3米深<ref name="USAT1" />。韋拉克鲁斯州沿海地区的多条高速公路同样被淹<ref name="RW1">{{cite news | author = Adventist Development and Relief Agency International | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2008-10-10 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Mexico: Heavy rains flood Tabasco and Veracruz, ADRA responds | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220849/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-heavy-rains-flood-tabasco-and-veracruz-adra-responds | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-heavy-rains-flood-tabasco-and-veracruz-adra-responds }}</ref>，另外还有250户民居因河流和湖泊洪水泛滥被淹<ref name="LJ1">{{cite news | author1 = A. Timoteo | author2 = R. Villalba | author3 = R. López | author4 = S. Ocampo | author5 = M. Habana | author6 = S. Maldonado y E. Argüelles | work = La Jornada | date = 2008-10-09 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Veracruz: causa Marco inundaciones y crecidas de ríos en 14 municipios | url = http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2008/10/09/index.php?section=estados&article=039n1est | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213718/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2008/10/09/index.php?section=estados&article=039n1est | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。韋拉克鲁斯州共有13个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]受到气旋影响。[[维加德亚拉托|维加德亚拉托]]（{{lang|en|Vega de Alatorre}}）有77人因家园被淹而被迫疏散到附近的避难所。米桑特拉和临近的科利帕（{{lang|en|Colipa}}）共发生3起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]事故，但都没有造成破坏。<ref>{{cite news |agency=Notimex |publisher=Millennium Publishing Group |date=2008-10-07 |accessdate=2008-10-11 |title=Tormenta "Marcos" afecta 13 municipios de Veracruz |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20081011082300/http://www.milenio.com/node/92356 |url=http://www.milenio.com/node/92356 |archivedate=2008-10-11 }}</ref>。马可总体上造成的影响很小，虽然受风暴影响的居民估计达到40万，但没有任何报道表明气旋曾直接导致人员伤亡，造成的破坏程度也很轻<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite news | agency = [[新华社|Xinhua News Agency]] | publisher = [[中国中央电视台|CCTV International]] | url = http://www.cctv.com/english/20081008/105420.shtml | date = 2008-10-07 | title = Tropical Storm Marco hits Mexican coast, 2,000 people evacuated | editor = Zhang Pengfei | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181215/http://www.cctv.com/english/20081008/105420.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-03-25 }}</ref>。

风暴过去后，墨西哥内政部民防总协调部宣布韋拉克鲁斯州的48个自治区进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125140817/https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/384476.causa-graves-danos-tormenta-marco-en-veracruz.html | agency = Notimex en Xalapa | work = El Siglo de Torreón | date = 2008-10-08 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Causa graves daños tormenta "Marco" en Veracruz | archivedate = 2016-01-25 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/384476.causa-graves-danos-tormenta-marco-en-veracruz.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | date = 2008-10-08 | title = Solicita Veracruz declaratoria de emergencia para 14 municipios | work = Revista Fundamentos}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Karla Cancino | website = ImagenDelGolfo.com.mx | location = Xalapa | date = 2008-11-11 | accessdate = 2012-02-24 | title = Flood, a Chronicle of Tragedy | archivedate = 2012-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120224080427/http://www.imagendelgolfo.com.mx/resumen.php?id=71722 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.imagendelgolfo.com.mx/resumen.php?id=71722 | publisher = Agencia Imagen del Golfo }}</ref>。到10月9日时，救灾物资已开始在灾区发放。根据墨西哥政府的纪录，发放的救灾物资包括4700张毛毯、2900张床垫、5554支瓶装水（容量均为500毫升）、26万盒牛奶、25万包饼干和1万2400箱学习用品。<ref>{{cite news | agency = Notimex en Xalapa | work = La Crónica de Hoy | date = 2008-10-09 | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | title = Continúa distribución de víveres a afectados por lluvias en Veracruz | url = http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2008/390026.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211848/http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2008/390026.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>

{{lang|en|UTC}}10月7日凌晨0点52分，马可的热带风暴强度风场半径仅有18.5公里，比1974年12月24日[[强烈热带气旋崔西|强烈热带气旋崔西]]所创的48公里纪录还要小一半以上，成为[[信史|有纪录以来]]规模最小的热带气旋并保持至今<ref name="FAQ" /><ref name="TCR" /><ref name="ATLHURDAT">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Atlantic Best Tracks, 1851 to 2008 | year = 2009 | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-03-25 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tra51to08.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185003/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tra51to08.txt | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref> 。
